#: ../../source/site/index.rst:54
msgid "User Directories"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/site/index.rst:56
msgid ""
"In addition to the global site-packages paths, ``site`` is responsible "
"for adding the user-specific locations to the import path. The user-"
"specific paths are all based on the ``USER_BASE`` directory, which "
"usually located in a part of the file system owned (and writable) by the "
"current user. Inside the ``USER_BASE`` directory is a ``site-packages`` "
"directory, with the path accessible as ``USER_SITE``."
msgstr ""

