#: ../../source/site/index.rst:84
msgid ""
"The user base directory can be set through the ``PYTHONUSERBASE`` "
"environment variable, and has platform-specific defaults "
"(``~/Python$version/site-packages`` for Windows and ``~/.local`` for non-"
"Windows)."
